name: "Cosmic Monster" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Felt pen on reclaimed cardboard with digital embellishments and a bit of digital drawing.] This is a minimalist exercise. How few lines can I use and still make an interesting image? (I hear you thinking, "A few more than THAT!" HA! Oh, that's funny...) ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
